item.description: Set up you own Nav Bar You have to change /config/_default/menus/menus.en.toml # [[docs]] # name = "Prologue" # weight = 10 # identifier = "prologue" # url = "/docs/prologue/" # [[docs]] # name = "Help" # weight = 60 # identifier = "help" # url = "/docs/help/" # [[docs]] # name = "Lorem" # weight = 70 # identifier = "lorem" # url = "/docs/lorem/" [[guide]] name = "Lorem" weight = 10 identifier = "lorem" url = "/guide/lorem/" [[tutorial]] name = "Lorem" weight = 10 identifier = "lorem" url = "/tutorial/lorem/" [[main]] name = "Docs" url = "/docs/" # url = "/docs/1.
